ALTER SESSION SET NLS_DATE_FORMAT = 'DD-MON-YYYY';
SET LINESIZE 250
SET PAGESIZE 200

--Drop Tables
DROP INDEX idx_rmls_rmno;
DROP TABLE TourOrdered;
DROP TABLE PackageComponent;
DROP TABLE PackageTour;
DROP TABLE Tour;
DROP TABLE Vehicle;
DROP TABLE AmenityOrdDet;
DROP TABLE AmenityOrdered;
DROP TABLE Amenity;
DROP TABLE AmenityCategory;
DROP TABLE RoomLeased;
DROP TABLE Room;
DROP TABLE RoomType;
DROP TABLE Payment;
DROP TABLE Reservation;
DROP TABLE PaymentType;
DROP TABLE Membership;
DROP TABLE Staff;
DROP TABLE Department;
DROP TABLE Guest;
DROP TABLE CorporateDiscount;


-- End of Drop tables
-- Drop Sequences

DROP SEQUENCE SEQ_ROOM_NO;
DROP SEQUENCE SEQ_ROOMLEASED_ID;
DROP SEQUENCE SEQ_PAYREF_NO;
DROP SEQUENCE SEQ_RESERV_NO;
DROP SEQUENCE SEQ_GUEST_ID;
DROP SEQUENCE SEQ_STAFF_NO;
DROP SEQUENCE SEQ_AORD_ID;
DROP SEQUENCE SEQ_AORDDET_ID;
DROP SEQUENCE SEQ_TORD_NO;

-- End of Drop Sequences
-- Create Tables

CREATE TABLE CorporateDiscount (
	CompanyCode 	CHAR(5) NOT NULL CHECK(LENGTH(CompanyCode) = 5),
	DiscountPct 	NUMBER(2) DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
        CompanyName     varchar(45) NOT NULL,
	Primary Key(CompanyCode)
);

CREATE SEQUENCE SEQ_GUEST_ID
START WITH 1
INCREMENT BY 1;

CREATE TABLE Guest (
	GuestID 	        char(5) NOT NULL,
	GuestName               varchar(30) NOT NULL,
	IDNo 			varchar(15) NOT NULL,
	EmailAddress 		varchar(30),
	ContactNumber 		varchar(13) not null,
	ResidenceStat 		char(1) DEFAULT 'L' CHECK(UPPER(ResidenceStat) IN ('L','F')) NOT NULL,
	IsMember 		char(1) DEFAULT 'N' CHECK(UPPER(IsMember) IN ('Y','N')) NOT NULL ,
	IsCorporateCustomer	char(1) DEFAULT 'N' CHECK(UPPER(IsCorporateCustomer) IN ('Y','N')) NOT NULL ,
	CompanyCode 		char(5) DEFAULT 'NOTAP' not null,
	Primary KEY(GuestID),
        FOREIGN KEY(CompanyCode) REFERENCES CorporateDiscount,
        constraint chk_guestName check (REGEXP_LIKE(GuestName ,  '^[A-Z a-z\s\-]+$')), 
	constraint chk_eml check (REGEXP_LIKE(EmailAddress,'^[a-zA-Z]\w+@(\S+)$')),
        constraint chk_contnum check (ContactNumber LIKE '60%' AND UPPER(ResidenceStat) = 'L' OR UPPER(ResidenceStat) = 'F'),
        constraint chk_idno check (REGEXP_LIKE(IDNo, '[0-9][0-9][0-1][0-9][0-3][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]') AND UPPER(ResidenceStat) = 'L' OR UPPER(ResidenceStat) = 'F')
);


CREATE TABLE Department (
	DeptCode      CHAR(3) not null,
        DeptName      VARCHAR(19) not null,
        Primary Key(DeptCode)
);

CREATE SEQUENCE SEQ_STAFF_NO
START WITH 1
INCREMENT BY 1;

CREATE TABLE Staff (
	StaffNo    char(4) not null,
        StaffName  varchar(30) not null,
        DeptCode   char(3) not null,
        ICNo       char(12) not null,
	PRIMARY KEY(StaffNo),
        constraint chk_icno check (REGEXP_LIKE(ICNo, '[0-9][0-9][0-1][0-9][0-3][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]'))     
);


CREATE TABLE Membership(
	GuestID                 char(5) NOT NULL,
	MemPoints 	        number(5) DEFAULT 0, 
	JoinDate 		date DEFAULT TO_DATE(SYSDATE, 'DD-MON-YYYY') not null,
	Primary key(GuestID),
        Foreign Key(GuestID) References Guest        
);

CREATE TABLE PaymentType(
	PayTypeCode 	char(4) not null,
	PayTypeName 	varchar(30) not null,
	Primary key(PayTypeCode)
);

CREATE SEQUENCE SEQ_RESERV_NO
START WITH 1
INCREMENT BY 1;

CREATE TABLE Reservation(
   ReservNo      CHAR(6) not null,
   GuestID       CHAR(5) not null,
   StaffNo       char(4) not null,
   ReservDate    DATE DEFAULT TO_DATE(SYSDATE, 'DD-MON-YYYY') not null ,
   ReservStat    CHAR(1) not null CHECK(UPPER(ReservStat) IN ('R','I','O','C')),
   PRIMARY KEY(ReservNo),
   FOREIGN KEY(GuestID) REFERENCES Guest,
   FOREIGN KEY(StaffNo) REFERENCES Staff
);

CREATE SEQUENCE SEQ_PAYREF_NO
START WITH 1
INCREMENT BY 1;

CREATE TABLE Payment (
	PayRefNo 	char(8) not null,
	ReservNo 	char(6) not null,
	StaffNo         char(4) not null,
	PayTypeCode 	char(4) not null,
	PayDate 	date DEFAULT TO_DATE(SYSDATE, 'DD-MON-YYYY') not null,
	PayAmt 		number(8,2) not null,
	Primary Key(PayRefNo),
	Foreign Key(PayTypeCode) References PaymentType(PayTypeCode),
        Foreign Key(ReservNo) References Reservation,
        Foreign Key(StaffNo) References Staff
);

CREATE TABLE RoomType (
   RoomTypeCode  CHAR(2) not null CHECK(LENGTH(RoomTypeCode) = 2),
   RoomTypeName  VARCHAR(18) not null,
   BedType       CHAR(2) not null CHECK(UPPER(BedType) IN ('SI', 'DO', 'QU', 'DX', 'KI')),
   RoomPrice     NUMBER(4) not null,
   MaxOccupants  NUMBER(1) not null,
   PRIMARY KEY(RoomTypeCode)
);

CREATE SEQUENCE SEQ_ROOM_NO
START WITH 1
INCREMENT BY 1;

CREATE TABLE Room (
   RoomNo        NUMBER(3) not null,
   RoomTypeCode  CHAR(2) not null,
   RoomFloor     NUMBER(2) not null,
   RoomStat      CHAR(1) DEFAULT 'A' not null CHECK(UPPER(RoomStat) IN ('A','O','R')),
   ViewType      VARCHAR(20) not null CHECK(UPPER(ViewType) IN ('RIVER VIEW', 'STREET VIEW', 'SEA VIEW', 'STREET VIEW', 'MOUNTAIN VIEW')),
   PRIMARY KEY(RoomNo),
   FOREIGN KEY(RoomTypeCode) REFERENCES RoomType
);

CREATE SEQUENCE SEQ_ROOMLEASED_ID
START WITH 1
INCREMENT BY 1;

CREATE TABLE RoomLeased(
   RoomLeasedID  NUMBER(4) not null,
   ReservNo      CHAR(6) not null,
   RoomNo        NUMBER(3) not null,
   CheckInDate   DATE not null,
   CheckOutDate  DATE not null,
   NoOccupants   NUMBER(1) not null,
   CONSTRAINT Chk_Room_Date CHECK(CheckOutDate > CheckInDate),
   PRIMARY KEY(RoomLeasedID),
   FOREIGN KEY(ReservNo) REFERENCES Reservation,
   FOREIGN KEY(RoomNo) REFERENCES Room
);

CREATE TABLE AmenityCategory (
   AmenityCatCode   char(4)   not null,
   AmenityCatName   varchar(25)  not null,
   Primary Key(AmenityCatCode)
);

CREATE TABLE Amenity (
   AmenityCode      char(4)   not null,
   AmenityCatCode   char(4)   not null,
   AmenityName      varchar(25)  not null,
   AmenityPrice     number(5,2) not null,
   primary key(AmenityCode),
   foreign key(AmenityCatCode) REFERENCES AmenityCategory
);


CREATE SEQUENCE SEQ_AORD_ID
START WITH 1
INCREMENT BY 1;

CREATE TABLE AmenityOrdered (
   AmenityOrdID   char(6)   not null,
   RoomLeasedID   number(4)   not null,
   OrdDate        date DEFAULT TO_DATE(SYSDATE, 'DD-MON-YYYY') not null,
   primary key(AmenityOrdID),
   foreign key(RoomLeasedID) references RoomLeased
);


CREATE SEQUENCE SEQ_AORDDET_ID
START WITH 1
INCREMENT BY 1;


CREATE TABLE AmenityOrdDet (
   AmenityOrdDetID  number(4) not null,
   AmenityOrdID     char(6) not null,
   AmenityCode      char(4) not null,
   AmenityQty       number(3) default 1 not null,
   primary key(AmenityOrdDetID),
   foreign key(AmenityOrdID) references AmenityOrdered,
   foreign key(AmenityCode) references Amenity   
);



CREATE TABLE Vehicle(
	VehicleRegNo	CHAR(15) not null,
	VehicleModel	VARCHAR(30) not null,
        VehicleType	VARCHAR(20) not null,
	MaxPassengers	NUMBER(2) not null,
	VehicleDesc	VARCHAR(50) not null,
	PRIMARY KEY(VehicleRegNo)
);

CREATE TABLE Tour (
	TourCode	CHAR(3) not null,	
	TourPrice	NUMBER(3) not null,
	TourDesc	VARCHAR(80) not null,
	MaxPeople	NUMBER(2) not null,
	Is3rdParty	CHAR(1) default 'N' not null CHECK(UPPER(Is3rdParty) IN ('Y','N')),
	IsPkg 		CHAR(1) default 'N' not null CHECK(UPPER(IsPkg) IN ('Y','N')),
	PRIMARY KEY(TourCode)
);

CREATE TABLE PackageTour (
	PkgCode		CHAR(3) not null,
	PRIMARY KEY(PkgCode)
);

CREATE TABLE PackageComponent(
	PkgCode		CHAR(3) not null,
	ComponentCode	CHAR(3) not null,
	PRIMARY KEY(PkgCode, ComponentCode),
	FOREIGN KEY(PkgCode) references packageTour(PkgCode),
        FOREIGN KEY(ComponentCode) references Tour(TourCode)
);

CREATE SEQUENCE SEQ_TORD_NO
START WITH 1
INCREMENT BY 1;

CREATE TABLE TourOrdered (
	TourOrderedNo	CHAR(5) not null,
	TourCode        CHAR(3) not null,
	ReservNo	CHAR(6) not null, 
	StaffNo		CHAR(4),
	VehicleRegNo	CHAR(15),
	TourDate	DATE not null,
	NoPerson	NUMBER(2) not null,
	PRIMARY KEY(TourOrderedNo),
	FOREIGN KEY(TourCode) REFERENCES Tour(TourCode),
	FOREIGN KEY(ReservNo) REFERENCES Reservation,
	FOREIGN KEY(StaffNo) REFERENCES Staff,
	FOREIGN KEY(VehicleRegNo) REFERENCES Vehicle(VehicleRegNo)
);

-- End of create tables

-- Create Index


CREATE INDEX idx_rmls_rmno
ON RoomLeased(RoomNo);


-- End of index


-- Create View

CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW Room_RoomType AS
select R.RoomTypeCode, RoomTypeName, RoomPrice, MaxOccupants, RoomNo, RoomFloor 
from Room R, RoomType T
where R.RoomTypeCode = T.RoomTypeCode
WITH READ ONLY CONSTRAINT read_only;


-- End of view

COMMIT;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfGuests
FROM Guest;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfMembers
FROM Membership;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfCorporateDiscounts
FROM CorporateDiscount;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfDepartments
FROM Department;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfStaffMembers
FROM Staff;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfReservations
FROM Reservation;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfRoomLeased
FROM RoomLeased;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfRooms
FROM Room;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfRoomTypes
FROM RoomType;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfAmenityOrders
FROM AmenityOrdered;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfAmenityOrderDetails
FROM AmenityOrdDet;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfAmenities
FROM Amenity;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfAmenityCategories
FROM AmenityCategory;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfTours
FROM Tour;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfPackageTours
FROM PackageTour;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfPackageComponents
FROM PackageComponent;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfTourOrders
FROM TourOrdered;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfVehicles
FROM Vehicle;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfPayments
FROM Payment;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS NoOfPaymentTypes
FROM PaymentType;
